result.adr_address: 13 Yuk Sau St, Happy Valley, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 13 Yuk Sau St, Happy Valley, Hong Kong
result.name: Classified Happy Valley

reviews.text:
This CLASSIFIED was a favourite of us for years when they arrived in Happy Valley ... Great staff team, enthusiasm and food made with love... 
NOW ... Feels that staff just don't want to be there ... Don't know hospitality and food and plating is just totally not nice nor a good experience... Really a pity...
Casual diner. Food quality is fine, I have a pastrami sandwich which is good while the pizza is just average. Services is good.
Good food (with lots to choose from) but average coffee.
Great food. Good service.

One of our faves although now doesn’t allow dogs even if you are sitting by the door and the dog is literally on the pavement? Surely the pavement is public space. Not sure who this grouch is making dogs banned from all cafes and restaurants. Miserable sod. Classified we still love you and love your food and smoothies but bring dogs back! X
